# ReactBits Component Registry for AkhAI

## Registry Configuration
When asked to add ReactBits components, fetch from: https://reactbits.dev/r/{component-name}.json

## Currently Installed Components (Custom Implementations)
Located in: `/packages/web/components/ui/`

### âœ… Installed Components:
1. **MagicBento.tsx** (247 lines)
   - Bento grid layout with framer-motion animations
   - Grey-only gradients for minimal design
   - Staggered fade-in effects
   - Size variants: small, medium, large

2. **FlowingMenu.tsx** (104 lines)
   - Animated navigation menu with moving background pill
   - Spring animations (stiffness: 500, damping: 30)
   - Active state: white background, black text
   - Hover state: grey-800 background

3. **GalaxyBackground.tsx** (96 lines)
   - Canvas-based star field with 150 twinkling stars
   - **GREYSCALE ONLY** - white to grey radial gradients
   - Sin wave animation for twinkle effect
   - Black background (#000000)

4. **DecryptedText.tsx** (88 lines)
   - Character-by-character reveal animation
   - Random character cycling before final text
   - Configurable speed (default 50ms)
   - Includes DecryptedTitle wrapper component

